casebody.data:
No. 14,153. Riss and Company, Inc. v. Spencer.

(.. P. [2d] ..)

Decided June 7, 1937. Rehearing denied June 28, 1937. Mr. John F. Mueller, for plaintiff in error. Messrs. Moffett & Hitchcock, for defendant in error.

Judgment affirmed in department on application for supersedeas without written opinion. Mr. Chief Justice Burke, Mr. Justice Hilliard and Mr. Justice Bakke participating.
